{"tid":1944249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土書店聯合書卷】集思廣益，罷買三中商，拒絕紅色書卷","createTime":"2020-03-26T09:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T19:30:46.000Z","uid":101260,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"876418cfafc23a194f1dab7cb7d50abe086008ac","tid":1944249,"uid":101260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"除左整合香港本土書店名單，我們有冇可能行多步，設立<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">本土書店聯合書卷</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n作為一個毒書撚，久唔久唔會收到親朋戚友轉贈三中商既書卷比我，所以有時都會無奈地入對家鋪買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但咁並唔代表我免費買書，因為賺左既喺三中商。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>書卷點來？大部份都喺向三中商比錢買！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得好少姐，幾張書卷豪比佢。其實賣書卷賺既錢你想像中多。<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>大大小小學界比賽獎品</strong>（最大sector應該喺呢到）<br />\n- 中小學獎學金（前派先用＄300換左表妹既進步獎書卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n- 私人贈禮、抽獎<br />\n<br />\n求其搵個例子計下數 Eg. <br />\n賽馬會「喜伴同行樂容融」繪畫比賽<br />\n冠軍――獎座乙個及書劵港幣1,000元<br />\n亞軍――獎座乙個及書劵港幣750元<br />\n季軍――獎座乙個及書劵港幣500元<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>加埋輕鬆超過＄2000</strong></span>（之前見到序言做義賣捐612基金，營業額都係＄8000+）<br />\n香港中小學啲立立雜雜既比賽多到你唔信。數學比賽 辯論比賽 音樂比賽 徵文 常識問答 標語填色...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dH4uFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dH4uFh.png&h=bcebfad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下呢個密密麻麻既中小學比賽日程表，估下三中商暗盤賺左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如有左本土書卷，至少大家可以<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>多個選擇，可以搶番個餅</strong></span>來做<br />\n而且家長如果收到呢d卷，以後識得上本土書店買書比小朋友，絕對一種對<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">本土書店既宣傳</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要發行本土書卷，至少有以下問題要解決：<br />\n加入準則：邊啲書店可以join，個標準喺咩<br />\n統一發行／運作模式：將書卷變書店間既次貨幣，解決A書店買卷，但B書店用卷既問題<br />\n利益分配問題：A書店收好多書卷，B書店完全無得益<br />\n防盜偽冒<br />\n宣傳<br />\n<br />\n作為一個書撚，呢個啲iea其實喺我腦入面一段時間，但呢派見到多左人討論本土書店，就認真諗下究竟可唔可行。暫時只喺諗到咁多，最苦惱個位暫時喺運作模式，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">想睇下大家點睇</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外分享，有巴打整咗個非三中商教科書店list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1311716/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1311716/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82e8478de99fc49d7657ac868b59965a65a9257","tid":1944249,"uid":101260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打搞過類似嘅兌換卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b9c55f2ce70c0cc8461589c669ddcc2f6e3113","tid":1944249,"uid":210351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"我舉腳支持呀<br />\n利申書蟲，一個月買幾本書"},{"pid":"7f8e7b18405733339309e7156663b133b1ab9d0c","tid":1944249,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"069c7fd2621f440a2b6506562953c1649aee9a3f","tid":1944249,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n平時上博客來多"},{"pid":"81cc1ff57edd3f0d2f53cb06db6e584235a95bc2","tid":1944249,"uid":101260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"069c7fd2621f440a2b6506562953c1649aee9a3f","tid":1944249,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n平時上博客來多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"用錯不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2137c29e8a3245e1b5c08a9f879d47a0196f828f","tid":1944249,"uid":52793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81cc1ff57edd3f0d2f53cb06db6e584235a95bc2","tid":1944249,"uid":101260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"069c7fd2621f440a2b6506562953c1649aee9a3f","tid":1944249,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy